data.description: Welcome to your ideal family home in Kilgore! This spacious home offers a surprisingly roomy 5,968 square feet of living space, making it perfect for entertaining with your family and friends. You'll find ample room for everyone, including four bedrooms, two and a half baths, and a three-car garage for your vehicles and storage needs. What truly sets this home apart is its ability to cater to your family's lifestyle. It features a rare indoor swimming pool, ensuring year-round fun and relaxation. Additionally, the property has two kitchens, allowing for simultaneous use and making it a breeze to host and prepare meals for gatherings. This home offers a generous amount of storage space to accommodate all your belongings, and the master bath comes with large closets, adding convenience to your daily routines. The sellers themselves have spoken highly of this home, making it their favorite among their previous residences. The open living areas create a welcoming and interconnected atmosphere, perfect for family time and entertaining. You'll love the neutral location for easy trips to both Kilgore and Longview! Don't miss the chance to make this versatile property your own. Call today to schedule a viewing and picture your family thriving in this spacious, all-encompassing home.
